    @FunctionalInterface
public interface AsLongStreamPlus
extends AsLongStreamPlusWithCalculate, AsLongStreamPlusWithConversion, AsLongStreamPlusWithCollect, AsLongStreamPlusWithForEach, AsLongStreamPlusWithGroupingBy, AsLongStreamPlusWithReduce, AsLongStreamPlusWithStatistic
